# Vendored W3C DPV release tree.
#
# Only Turtle (.ttl) files consumed by scripts/ are tracked, plus the
# examples HTML file used by scripts/gen_dpvcg_turtle.py.  All other
# serialisations (HTML, JSON-LD, N3, OMN, RDF/XML, CSV) and static assets
# carry the same information or are not required; they are ignored to keep
# the repo small.
#
# Scripts that read from upstream-releases/:
#   - scripts/dpv_core_to_linkml.py
#       dpv/dpv/dpv-owl.ttl       (aggregate OWL ontology — identity)
#       dpv/dpv/dpv.ttl           (aggregate canonical/SKOS — enrichment)
#       dpv/dpv/modules/*-owl.ttl (per-module OWL ontology — identity)
#       dpv/dpv/modules/*.ttl     (per-module canonical/SKOS — enrichment)
#   - scripts/dpv_csv_to_sssom.py
#       mappings/<source>/dpv-<source>.csv   (kept as-is; sibling tree)
#   - scripts/dpv_27560_to_linkml.py
#       ../schema/dpv-27560.ttl   (outside upstream-releases/)
#   - scripts/gen_dpvcg_turtle.py
#       dpv/examples/dex.html     (DPV examples HTML — Turtle snippets embedded
#                                  as <pre> blocks; no stand-alone E*.ttl in the
#                                  upstream release archive)
#   - scripts/dpv_extensions_to_linkml.py
#       dpv/<ext>/<ext>-owl.ttl          (per-extension aggregate OWL)
#       dpv/<ext>/<ext>.ttl              (per-extension aggregate canonical)
#       dpv/<ext>/modules/*-owl.ttl      (per-extension per-module OWL)
#       dpv/<ext>/modules/*.ttl          (per-extension per-module canonical)
#       (and recursively for nested extensions such as legal/eu/gdpr/)
#
# Strategy: ignore all non-Turtle serialisations and static assets under dpv/;
# let every .ttl file be tracked naturally across the whole tree.
# This avoids having to enumerate every extension directory explicitly and
# automatically covers new extensions added in future upstream releases.
dpv/**/*.html
dpv/**/*.jsonld
dpv/**/*.n3
dpv/**/*.rdf
dpv/**/*.omn
dpv/**/*.csv
dpv/**/*.js
dpv/**/*.css
dpv/**/*.png
dpv/**/*.gif
dpv/**/*.svg
dpv/**/*.ico
dpv/**/*.bpmn
dpv/**/*.drawio
dpv/**/*.plantuml
dpv/**/*.org
dpv/**/*.sh
# Re-include dex.html (needed by scripts/gen_dpvcg_turtle.py to extract
# Turtle snippets embedded as <pre> blocks in the DPV examples page).
!dpv/examples/dex.html
